    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuideHub!  To change color on click of mui chip in react js, you can use  state variable. it will change color on click of mui chip‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! </p>\n<p>To change color on click of mui chip in react js, you can use <code class=\"language-text\">chipColor</code> state variable. it will change color on click of mui chip in React JS.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, How to change color on click of mui chip in react js.</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the following packages to use mui chip in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npm install @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">yarn add @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install MUI and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import Material-UI chip.</li>\n<li>Use the chip Component</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Step 1: Install MUI and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import Material-UI chip.</h3>\n<p>After installing <code class=\"language-text\">MUI</code>, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Chip <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useState <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Use the chip Component</h3>\n<p>You can use the <code class=\"language-text\">chip</code> component in your react js. For example, Chips allow users to enter information, make selections, filter content, or initiate actions. You can use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;chip></code> component make a chip in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Chip\n  color<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>chipColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Clickable Chip\"</span>\n  onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>MUI material change color on click of mui chip example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example, you need to import <code class=\"language-text\">chip</code> Component. you can use <code class=\"language-text\">handleClick</code> function and to change color on click of mui chip in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Chip <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useState <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">App</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>chipColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setChipColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'primary'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">handleClick</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>chipColor <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'primary'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">setChipColor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'secondary'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">setChipColor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'primary'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Chip\n      color<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>chipColor<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Clickable Chip\"</span>\n      onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">@mui/material</code> component and changed color on click of mui chip in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 299px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a289d3996d7f9c71893cfe7b225191bf/cf880/color-on-click.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.16455696202532%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRl4AAABXRUJQVlA4IFIAAABwAwCdASoUAAsAPtFWo0uoJKMhsAgBABoJYgCdACHRvGUSEAAA/VOgYALYPcxsul7bcv7uu6z+jisOLwyuL75eYnbTtxRzINWq3GuzVh2exAAA'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, Mui, color, on, click\"\n        title=\"React, Mui, color, on, click\"\n        src=\"/static/a289d3996d7f9c71893cfe7b225191bf/cf880/color-on-click.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a289d3996d7f9c71893cfe7b225191bf/81b7c/color-on-click.webp 158w,\n/static/a289d3996d7f9c71893cfe7b225191bf/cf880/color-on-click.webp 299w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 299px) 100vw, 299px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Here, we are provided code sandbox links for the above program change color on click of mui chip in react js. Then you can use whenever you want and do the changes as per your requirements.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aguidehub.com/codesandbox/?code=tender-alex-4wd26s\" rel=\"nofollow\"  target=\"_BLANK\" >Try it Yourself</a></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to change color on click of mui chip in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"July 12, 2023","description":"Example of change color on click of mui chip in React js with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"media/template/reactjs.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add end  icon of mui chip in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2023-07-13-how-to-add-end-icon-of-mui-chip-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to make mui chip disabled in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2023-07-12-how-to-make-mui-chip-disabled-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2023-07-12-how-to-change-color-on-click-of-mui-chip-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2023-07-13-how-to-add-end-icon-of-mui-chip-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2023-07-12-how-to-make-mui-chip-disabled-in-react-js/"}},
